| ShortSummary = One of the company's clients needs a large order of duck calls, but Willie has trouble finding anyone to help fill it. Jase and Phil draft him for a late-night frog hunting trip, Korie pulls Phil and Miss Kay in to film a cooking DVD, and Jase decides to flood the loading dock and use it as a test pond for trying out new calls on actual ducks.
