| ShortSummary= With the big Robertson family football game coming up, Phil gets his grandchildren to help set up the field. Willie goes overboard with his training regimen and hits Korie in the face with a pass. When Jase thinks he can be just as good a CEO as Willie, Willie gives him the job for the day, leaving him and Si to try to deliver a truckload of duck calls to a client on short notice.
| LineColor =B3C1CF
}}
