| ShortSummary= A large order is placed at Duck Commander, and in order to keep up, Jase and the other employees decide to build a conveyor belt. The work goes less well than planned until Miss Kay uses a favorite old trick of hers. Meanwhile, Phil and Si declare war against the beavers who are disrupting their duck hunting and call John Luke in to help deliver the final blow.
| LineColor =B3C1CF
}}
| EpisodeNumber =4
| EpisodeNumber2 =4
