| EpisodeNumber2 =13
| Viewers =2.05
| ShortSummary= Jase tricks Willie into letting him use the Duck Commander RV, and he brings Jep, Martin, and Si along for a road trip. Meanwhile, chaos is caused when Willie finds an alligator in Phil and Miss Kay's yard.
| LineColor =B3C1CF
}}
| EpisodeNumber =14
| EpisodeNumber2 =14
| Viewers =2.31
| ShortSummary = The Robertson men and women compete in their annual turkey cook-off, with Phil judging each side's recipes. Jase and Si go hunting to bring in the birds for the competition, using decoys that prove a little too effective, and Phil makes a few unwanted "renovations" around the Duck Commander office that include taking down all the doors.
| LineColor =B3C1CF
}}
