| EpisodeNumber2 =15
| Viewers=2.56
| ShortSummary= When Willie is offered another job, he takes the Duck Commander crew on an employee retreat in order to help him figure out what to do. However, things quickly turn sour when the men find that Willie has taken them to a team-building camp and ridicule him ceaselessly for it.
| LineColor =B3C1CF
}}
}}
